McDonald’s Names Ramaphosa as South African Licensee

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-17T10:34:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/mcdonald-s-names-ramaphosa-as-south-african-licensee-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling of McDonald’s in first paragraph.)    McDonald’s Corp. (MCD)  named Cyril Ramaphosa as developmental licensee for  South Africa .  Ramaphosa will be responsible for the operation of
McDonald’s restaurants in South Africa, the company said in an
e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at   areed12@bloomberg.net  